    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Backrooms Lost Runners</strong> 是一款合作生存恐怖游戏，挑战你和你的朋友直面内心最深的恐惧。每个环境都充满了危险、谜团和意想不到的变数。只有通过无缝的团队协作和对细节的高度关注，你才能生存下来并揭开后室的秘密。 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072120/extras/eb0cf85c943a0a4c8123d800d7c7d398.avif?t=1768582721\" width=616 height=198 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸式氛围</strong> 穿越昏暗的走廊，体验动态灯光与真实音效设计。在这个世界里，每一步——甚至每一句低语——都可能是最后一次。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>挑战性的逻辑谜题</strong> 解开一系列基于电路、开关和密码的谜题。每个挑战都会根据你团队的方式进行适配，要求你灵活思考和创造性解决问题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072120/extras/2e4fa5377f719beb2f4c6d6a419caa1d.poster.avif?t=1768582721\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072120/extras/2e4fa5377f719beb2f4c6d6a419caa1d.webm?t=1768582721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072120/extras/2e4fa5377f719beb2f4c6d6a419caa1d.mp4?t=1768582721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>适应性威胁</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对对声音、光线和动作做出反应的独特实体。有些怪物会追踪你的声音，而另一些则在黑暗中默默潜伏。了解它们的行为模式，才能始终领先一步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072120/extras/98b2a50f17c407297b718c5c2377957a.poster.avif?t=1768582721\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072120/extras/98b2a50f17c407297b718c5c2377957a.webm?t=1768582721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072120/extras/98b2a50f17c407297b718c5c2377957a.mp4?t=1768582721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>理智机制</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >监控你的精神状态：靠近热源或光源可以减缓理智值的下降。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>四维空间的死后世界</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >死亡只是开始。死后你将置身于一个超现实的四维空间中，你唯一的目标就是回到人间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072120/extras/697341d2ff2b49f9d7dae0092f0042d7.poster.avif?t=1768582721\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072120/extras/697341d2ff2b49f9d7dae0092f0042d7.webm?t=1768582721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072120/extras/697341d2ff2b49f9d7dae0092f0042d7.mp4?t=1768582721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>真正的合作玩法</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合作对生存至关重要。管理资源，通过语音聊天协调战术，并集体做出决策。 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072120/extras/8f24afd3d2101e51d89e5b0884e85a65.avif?t=1768582721\" width=616 height=198 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>剧情与任务系统</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过发现散落的日记、录音日志和U盘，拼凑出灾难的时间线。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072120/extras/7cc03faca2b7fa3e7890bb2bd9d0bff9.poster.avif?t=1768582721\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072120/extras/7cc03faca2b7fa3e7890bb2bd9d0bff9.webm?t=1768582721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072120/extras/7cc03faca2b7fa3e7890bb2bd9d0bff9.mp4?t=1768582721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072120/extras/d13f5e05bc8d0c269d6ff54dbb20c287.poster.avif?t=1768582721\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072120/extras/d13f5e05bc8d0c269d6ff54dbb20c287.webm?t=1768582721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072120/extras/d13f5e05bc8d0c269d6ff54dbb20c287.mp4?t=1768582721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>资源管理与角色成长</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搜集食物、衣物和工具，以维持生命值、体力和理智。你会孤身冒险寻找高价值战利品，还是紧跟团队脚步？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索营地、储物柜和避难所，寻找宝贵物品和资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072120/extras/a0657f96a9e8e7f9f2cc533532034118.poster.avif?t=1768582721\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072120/extras/a0657f96a9e8e7f9f2cc533532034118.webm?t=1768582721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072120/extras/a0657f96a9e8e7f9f2cc533532034118.mp4?t=1768582721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>扭曲现实的异常现象</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小心零重力区域、突然出现的传送门和不断变化的墙壁。在后室中，物理法则也不再适用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072120/extras/fbc59e4b979bfa989b7c8e94f2f66f62.poster.avif?t=1768582721\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072120/extras/fbc59e4b979bfa989b7c8e94f2f66f62.webm?t=1768582721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072120/extras/fbc59e4b979bfa989b7c8e94f2f66f62.mp4?t=1768582721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>你的冒险才刚刚开始。</u></strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072120/extras/98e65517cdbc52a9132218eaca46db67.avif?t=1768582721\" width=616 height=198 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>将游戏加入愿望单 —— 原因如下！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Backrooms Lost Runners 融合了惊悚的恐怖体验、烧脑的谜题以及深度的合作玩法，构建出一个不断演进的冒险世界。更多地图、生物、制作系统、基地建设与全新机制即将到来，将本游戏添加至你的愿望单，即可第一时间获取更新信息。</p>",
